{"tid":1356894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【人手置頂】報料時請用哩個Apps影相/片","createTime":"2019-07-23T15:15:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T12:25:12.000Z","uid":34604,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"498ef663924d2b04ea335f5e6b888943c8b8bd1c","tid":1356894,"uid":34604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:15:42.000Z","msg":"岩岩開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>幫手傳出去</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n鑒於謠言滿天飛 為免資訊混亂<br />\n報料時用以下App影相/片，會自動顯示時間<br />\n方便Fact Check<br />\n個Apps無上傳權限，可以放心資訊唔會流出<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">Timestamp camera</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>效果：</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6rpyO7x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6rpyO7x.png&h=5aeeec9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n至少真係要謠傳消息既人<br />\n要偽造時間地點都要一定既時間<br />\n<br />\n如果打後有人要拎番舊相/片出黎<br />\n都要搵方法/時間之前既清水印<br />\n-<br />\nIOS: <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/timestamp-camera-basic/id840110184?l=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Ftimestamp-camera-basic%2Fid840110184%3Fl%3Den&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4WCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=7f6fc432\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/timestamp-camera-basic/id840110184?l=en</a><br />\n<br />\nANROID: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.jeyluta.timestampcamerafree&amp;hl=en_US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.jeyluta.timestampcamerafree%26hl%3Den_US&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4WCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=f62c4819\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.jeyluta.timestampcamerafree&amp;hl=en_US</a>"},{"pid":"48ea42511c